snippet.title: ✏️ 25 Questions with ONE OF US IS LYING Author Karen McManus
snippet.description:
We got the chance to ask Karen McManus 25 questions all about writing and her fantastic book One Of Us Is Lying (which she has described as The Breakfast Club with Murder). Thanks for watching!

Check out One Of Us Is Lying: http://po.st/OneOfUsIsLying

Find her online:
https://www.twitter.com/writerkmc
http://www.instagram.com/writerkmc
